{"tid":135203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]吳克儉仲有家人未死","createTime":"2017-02-26T07:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T08:38:12.000Z","uid":56524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a95552cc4c413ca085961bf6be9ce4d41a5d59","tid":135203,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:30:41.000Z","msg":"吳克儉將退休 冀可陪家人及每月讀30本書<br />\n<br />\n教育局局長吳克儉首次表明不會留任下屆政府，將會退休。他希望退休後可陪家人及每月閱讀30本書。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否與自己民望低有關，吳克儉說，聽到不同的批評，但不認同指他強推國民教育科的指控。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/吳克儉將退休-冀可陪家人及每月讀30本書-042754467.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E5%90%B3%E5%85%8B%E5%84%89%E5%B0%87%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-%E5%86%80%E5%8F%AF%E9%99%AA%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%8A%E6%AF%8F%E6%9C%88%E8%AE%8030%E6%9C%AC%E6%9B%B8-042754467.html&d=4HHrVRRB2qdXUamIokVXjTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=461ed093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/吳克儉將退休-冀可陪家人及每月讀30本書-042754467.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b2c3ec47adf8a4e7a77d8cd7ebaf1d5adbad02","tid":135203,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:32:38.000Z","msg":"吳克儉定羅范椒芬賤啲"},{"pid":"5c36b59a9367208e30e5a711cdc71dd1cb5c4be3","tid":135203,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"落去陪唔得咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8d18342c54f2a81d6577431b634113f491b1c8","tid":135203,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T08:20:22.000Z","msg":"1. 叫佢快D去陪老婆老母<br />\n<br />\n2. 質疑佢仲有屋企人<br />\n<br />\n邊一